{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_06_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 実家に来る？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――大阪、合同カウントダウンライブ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The joint countdown live at Osaka",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんな、沢山のエール\nありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To all the fans‚\nthank you so much for the many cheers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "今年最後のステージを、こうしてみんなと\n迎えることが出来て、私達は幸せです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're happy that we could spend the last stage\nof this year with everyone like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ、はぁ、良かった。無事だったんだな\n莉央さんが来ないって聞いた時は驚いたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huff‚ huff. I'm relieved. You're safe.\nI was surprised when I heard you weren't coming‚ Rio-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それから……今更だけど、遅刻してごめんなさい\n遅刻は、この後のパフォーマンスで挽回します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… It's late to say this now‚ but I'm sorry for being late.\nI'll make up for it with my performance afterward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "精一杯、みんなのために歌うから聴いて下さい！\n『最高優美ロンリネス』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll sing my heart out for everyone!\n\"Saiko-yuubi Loneliness\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5600.000000000002,
          "startTime": 37.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4899.999999999998,
          "startTime": 41
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.6666667,
          "startTime": 40.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、カウントダウンライブ、お疲れ様でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ great job on the countdown live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　ちょ、ちょっと{user}さん\nどうしてここにいるの？　今、東京のはずじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Wait‚ {user}-san‚ why are you here?\nYou should be in Tokyo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、急にライブバトルが決まったじゃないですか\nそれに莉央さんが行方不明だって言うし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ a live battle was suddenly scheduled‚\nand you were reported missing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……その、迷惑を掛けたわね……\n……本当にごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that's… I caused trouble…\nI'm really sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "事情は聞きましたから。それに\nトラブルが吹き飛ぶくらい、最高のステージでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard about the situation. Besides‚\nyour performance was so incredible that it blew away any troubles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、本当にいろんなことがあったけど……\n一年の最後に、最高のパフォーマンスが出来たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ there were many things that happened‚ but…\nwe could deliver the best performance ever at year-end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、莉央さんも、他のみんなも\nこれ以上ないくらい力強いステージングでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ both Rio-san and the rest of the group gave a\npowerful performance that couldn't be surpassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。来年のLizNoirには\nもっと期待してくれていいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. I bet you can expect more from\nLizNoir next year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達なら、BIG4入りだって出来るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With us now‚ we can aim for the top 4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、一緒にトップを獲りにいきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ let's aim for the top together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってくれて嬉しいわ\n少し早いけど、今年一年、とてもお世話になったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm happy that you said that.\nIt's a bit early‚ but I've been greatly indebted to you this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "来年もよろしく頼むわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm counting on you next year too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそ。それと、年始はオフもありますし\nゆっくり休んで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Likewise. Also‚ you have some days off at the beginning of the year‚\nso please take your time to rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "この時期に休みが取れるなんて、何年ぶりかしら\nバンプロ時代は年中、休みなんてなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't believe I can take a break at this time of the year.\nIt's been years since I had a break during my Van Prods days.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんの実家は岡山でしたよね？\n大阪から近いですし、お正月は帰省したらどうです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ your family's in Okayama‚ right?\nIt's close to Osaka‚ so how about spending New Year's there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、さっきお母さんとは会ったけど\n話をする時間はあまりなかったし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ I met my mother earlier‚\nbut we didn't have much time to talk…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロへの移籍の話も、ちゃんと出来てなかったわ\n明日、このまま実家に帰るのもいいかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I haven't talked about transfer to Hoshimi Prods either.\nMaybe I better just go back home tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、明日の新幹線、俺が手配しておきますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I'll book the Shinkansen for tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　オフの面倒まで見なくてもいいわよ\n貴方だって忙しいんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? You don't have to take care of my day off.\nAren't you busy too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、俺も正月休みを取ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm also taking a New Year's break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が休日を？　仕事が恋人の貴方が？\nさては休日出勤するつもりね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're taking a day off? Even though your lover is your job?\nI see‚ you're planning to work on your day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことしませんよ……俺をなんだと思ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't do that… What do you think of me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "仕事人間でしょ\nまぁいいわ。それで、休日はどうやって過ごすの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're a workaholic‚ right?\nWell‚ fine. So‚ how are you planning to spend your day off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりに思い切り寝ようかと。寝正月です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm thinking of sleeping as long as I can. It's a \"Sleep New Year.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
