      "text": "それじゃリフレッシュにならないでしょ\n何かやりたいことはないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That won't be refreshing at all.\nDon't you have anything you want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……特に思いつきませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I can't think of anything in particular.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ旅行なんていいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ how about going on a trip?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
