      "text": "それくらい自分で考えなさい\n私だって、人に勧められるほど詳しい場所は知らないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think of it yourself.\nI don't know places well enough to recommend you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 202.4666666667
    },
    {
