      "text": "地元の岡山なら案内出来るけど……\nそうだ、なんなら私の実家に来る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can guide you around my hometown of Okayama‚ though…\nActually‚ how about coming to my parents' house?",
        "id": ""
